title: London, BL, Add. 14674
Psalms according to the Peshitta version
Psalms, according to the Peshitta version, divided into ܩܬܝܣ̈ܡܛܐ (καθίσματα) and ܫܘܒ̈ܚܐ, according to the custom of the Greek church.
